
Tek.Gadg video interview via http://www.tekgadg.com/tekgadg/2011/5/15/tekgadg-interview-ethan-zuckerman-chi-2011.html


=Description=

"[[Ethan Zuckerman]] is a senior researcher at the Berkman Center for Internet and Society at Harvard University. He talked to us about his contribution to the invention of pop-up ads (!), free expression on the internet, and democratization of publishing.

He is also a co-founder of Global Voices, which reports what is going on in the global blogosphere. You can follow him at @EthanZ, and read his blog http://www.ethanzuckerman.com/blog/ ."


